# ClojureScript Frontend

## UI

- **Reagent** components in `galaticos.components.*`
- No React hooks, no JSX — Hiccup-style vectors in `.cljs`
- Shared primitives: `src-cljs/galaticos/components/common.cljs`

## Routing

- `src-cljs/galaticos/routes.cljs` — reitit-frontend
- Effects/API side effects: `effects.cljs`

## Data

- HTTP: `src-cljs/galaticos/api.cljs`
- App state: `src-cljs/galaticos/state.cljs`

## Styling

- Tailwind utility classes on `:class`
- Follow existing light/dark patterns (`dark:` variants)

## Build

- Config: `shadow-cljs.edn`
- Do not hand-edit `resources/public/js/compiled/` or `public/js/compiled/`
- CSS output: `resources/public/css/app.css` (built from Tailwind/PostCSS)

## Charts

Recharts via CLJS wrappers in `components/charts.cljs` — keep data shape aligned with API responses.
